scalar}{\cf1\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs28\loch\f3
, i.e. the idea that sequences of notes, played sequentially\~  }{\cf1\i\ai\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs28\loch\f3
within a given scale}{\cf1\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs28\loch\f3
