global thematic}{\cf1\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs28\loch\f3
, i.e. the experience, of a person with EVP, that a melody played in a major or minor scale is specifically\~  }{\cf1\i\ai\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs28\loch\f3
